Task::Twitter

This module is a "task", which currently installs Net::Twitter,
Log::Dispatch::Twitter, Twitter::TagGrep, WWWW:ItsABot and Net::PingFM . If
you want your Twitter-related module included, let me know.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Task::Twitter

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Task::Twitter

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Task::Twitter

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Task::Twitter

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Task::Twitter


